platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Venture deep into mysterious woods in this innovative adventure.
了無人煙的冰雪森林，冒出各樣怪奇生物，最可怕的，卻是終點盡頭的未來。
Venture deep into mysterious woods in this innovative adventure.
對隔離島的調查，竟成了超現實的生存冒險，保持冷靜才能走出危機。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The eclectic studio behind Bumpy Road stretches its creative wings once again with riveting results in this haunting first-person adventure game. Whether we're tracking a path in the snowy wilderness or piecing together the creepy storyline, the Year Walk experience overflows with style and atmospheric allure.
